###########################
#  Initialization

DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
"PGstandard.pl",
"MathObjects.pl",
"AnswerFormatHelp.pl",
"PGML.pl",
"PGcourse.pl",
"contextFraction.pl",
);

TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;


###########################
#  Setup

# Parameters
$a = random(1,3);   # different variations of problem

$u = random(2,5);  
$v = random(6,10);  
$w = random(1,7);

# Solution
if ($a == 1) {
  $x1 = List("none");
}
elsif ($a == 2) {
  $x1 = $v + $u;
  if (($x1^2 - $v*$x1) <= 0) {
    $x1 = List("none");
  }
  $x1 = List($x1);
}
else{
  $x1 = $v + $u;
  if (($x1^2 - $v*$x1 + $w) <= 0) {
      $x1 = List(0);
  } 
  else {
      $x1 = List(0, $x1);
  }
}

Context()->strings->add(
  "none"=>{},
  "no solution"=>{alias=>"none"}
);

###########################
#  Main text

if ($a == 1) {
BEGIN_PGML

Give all solutions to the equation, or state that there are no solutions by entering "NONE".  

If there is more than one solution, enter the answers as a comma-separated list.


[` \ln \left( - {[$u]} x \right) = \ln \left( x^2 - {[$v]} x \right) `]  

[_______________]{$x1} [@ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") @]*

END_PGML
}
elsif ($a == 2) {
BEGIN_PGML

Give all solutions to the equation, or state that there are no solutions by entering "NONE".  

If you find more than one solution, enter your answer as a comma-separated list.

[` \ln \left( {[$u]} x \right) = \ln \left( x^2 - {[$v]} x \right) `]  

[_______________]{$x1} [@ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") @]*

END_PGML
}
else {
BEGIN_PGML

Give all solutions to the equation, or state that there are no solutions by entering "NONE".

If you find more than one solution, enter your answer as a comma-separated list.

[` \ln \left( {[$u]} x + {[$w]} \right) = \ln \left( x^2 - {[$v]} x + {[$w]} \right) `]  

[_______________]{$x1} [@ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") @]*

END_PGML
}

